      <title>特朗普瞄准了南希·佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）珍视的旧金山公园</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/trump-takes-aim-at-san-francisco-s-presidio-treasured-by-nancy-pelosi</link>
